.git-nested-backup/

# Dependencies and generated outputs
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/.angular/cache/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.downloadIntermediates/
**/.temp/

# Local environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

